<a href="https://www.instagram.com/secretpostofficeofficial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">秘密邮局</a>运送包裹，这项免费服务允许音乐节观众向现场的其他人发送信件和卡片。</p><p>五年后，麦克斯在《大月亮》的演出中身着邮局制服走上舞台，在秘密邮局工作人员的簇拥下向杰克逊求婚——请看下面的那一刻。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">所以这件事发生了…… <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/8i7luXxn29">pic.twitter.com/8i7luXxn29</a></p><p> — 大月亮 (@thebigmoon) <a href="https://twitter.com/thebigmoon/status/1162817069248864256?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2019 年 8 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>现在，为了让联系更圆满，这对夫妇在布雷肯比肯斯的格拉努斯克公园举办的音乐节举办地喜结连理，周围都是朋友、家人和绿人邮政工作人员。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-z1Kq4umnn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: